window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A stand-alone entry in the Dangerous Doms series.</p> <p>When I knew Aisling, she was my sister's best friend. Young. Innocent. Wild.</p> <p>But that was then.</p> <p>Now I'm hardened and ruthless. A bare-knuckle boxer. An enforcer for the Clan. And that carefree girl is a slave to her addictions with demons in her eyes. And I want her.</p> <p>When she witnesses a murder - a murder I committed - I have no choice but to take her.</p> <p>I'll keep her silent. I'll keep her hostage. I'll see her freed from her addictions.</p> <p>And then I'll keep her bound to me...forever.</p>"; 
